---
title: Tuscan Beef & Roast Vegetables with Béarnaise Sauce
description: One of the many reasons to love cooking is that it can transport you. Even if you haven't got a holiday coming up, this dish of tender sliced beef strips draped over Tuscan style roast veggies and crunchy ciabatta bread croutons will conjure up visions of an Italian farmhouse in pastoral fields. Buon Appetito!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bb41c90ae08b569934e9bf3-b6e9ce36.jpg
